{"tid":2134223,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政府指竹篙灣檢疫營設計風速高於十號颶風信號陣風風速","createTime":"2020-07-31T14:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T14:46:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"86af0798f842a3d9c1b1a3f12c764ae4c78ed7b6","tid":2134223,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:14:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541130-20200731.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541130-20200731.htm&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=70939e18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541130-20200731.htm&h=41cce354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541130-20200731.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n土木工程拓展署及建築署表示，竹篙灣檢疫營舍是按屋宇署《香港風力效應作業守則》而設計，所採用的設計風速高於香港天文台十號颶風信號的陣風風速。<br />\n<br />\n對於有報道關注檢疫營的工程能否抵禦強風，署方回應指，第一期工程，均在全程監管下進行，並根據相關質量及程序要求驗收。<br />\n<br />\n檢疫營舍以「組裝合成」建築法分別興建100個和700個檢疫單位，單位柱底與石屎底座以螺絲帽及相關組件建造接駁，以便於裝拆，並能有效控制其質量。"},{"pid":"4226ace895dfef0a216202dbf4822a4ab43c5c1c","tid":2134223,"uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:15:32.000Z","msg":"質量係mass<br />\n品質係quality<br />\n<br />\n不過，佢講mass又唔可以話錯"},{"pid":"dd0fb0786d18a49adf9fafbbc9613a84d2f71197","tid":2134223,"uid":273703,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:16:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5d935c73d94836ae6e4ba99d9dcab46dd538938","tid":2134223,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd0fb0786d18a49adf9fafbbc9613a84d2f71197","tid":2134223,"uid":273703,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:16:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmo